ght still pass. Check eval.py's determinism requirements. Proceed cautiously.\nCommands: list files; cat eval.py; cat model_ref.xml; run eval.py baseline; create model.xml copy; edit model.xml with safe options (sizes, threads, disabling visual); run eval.py to test; iterate.",
